name: Warp dash - post jam version
description:
In warp dash, you are making a voyage in space but are attacked!

The enemy has hacked your controls to make your laser fire button speed up time!

How long can you fend off the hordes of enemy ships?

W, A, S, D to move and click to shoot.

Code : haddle

art : haddle

sfx : made with sfxr

music : dev_dino

Check out the jam version that was made in 48 hours (i only used 2 of the 3 days)
